1582
02:11:06,234 --> 02:11:07,526
Hey!

1583
02:12:11,048 --> 02:12:12,507
Excuse me.

1584
02:14:01,200 --> 02:14:02,867
Come here.

1585
02:14:02,952 --> 02:14:06,037
He's in that first door.
I'm going around the front.

1586
02:16:54,290 --> 02:16:57,584
You sick son of a bitch!

1587
02:17:29,033 --> 02:17:31,534
Well, of course I can talk.
Why, isn't that what I'm doing?

1588
02:17:31,660 --> 02:17:33,870
I mean, if it's something else,
please advise me, Maury.

1589
02:17:33,996 --> 02:17:37,040
I always like to learn something
