1590
02:17:37,166 --> 02:17:39,584
I swear to you, Joey, every fucking
lawyer on the face of the earth

1591
02:17:39,668 --> 02:17:41,252
ought to be killed.

1592
02:17:41,337 --> 02:17:44,380
You want to what?
You want to meet with McDeere?

1593
02:17:44,506 --> 02:17:47,759
