1665
02:22:49,895 --> 02:22:52,688
Like Yasir-fucking-Arafat, huh?

1666
02:22:53,232 --> 02:22:55,650
Never a night in the same place.

1667
02:22:57,319 --> 02:23:00,238
In any case,
I need your written authorization,

1668
02:23:00,322 --> 02:23:04,408
so I can release your bills,
like every other client has given.

1669
02:23:09,998 --> 02:23:12,917
You have this authorization with you?

1670
02:23:13,001 --> 02:23:14,293
I do.

1671
02:23:37,401 --> 02:23:39,652
- Anything in there?
- Nothing.

1672
02:23:43,073 --> 02:23:44,115
Fuck!

1673
02:23:44,908 --> 02:23:48,744
You got the account number?
You know how to access it?

1674
02:23:48,829 --> 02:23:50,204
