that the money's there.

1675
02:23:50,289 --> 02:23:52,081
$750,000.

1676
02:23:52,165 --> 02:23:54,750
I love your crooked little mouth.

1677
02:24:03,427 --> 02:24:05,428
Well, it's not my best feature.

1678
02:24:05,554 --> 02:24:07,138
Wow!

1679
02:24:08,807 --> 02:24:09,932
Well, what is?

1680
02:24:33,248 --> 02:24:35,291
Where the hell are you?

1681
02:24:42,507 --> 02:24:44,800
