they aren't the bad guys.

1688
02:24:57,105 --> 02:24:59,148
Ask the Moroltos who's harder to find,

1689
02:24:59,274 --> 02:25:01,233
the killer or the lawyer
who hides their money.

1690
02:25:01,318 --> 02:25:02,360
