in fines.

1712
02:25:50,867 --> 02:25:52,868
That's more than you had on Capone.

1713
02:25:52,994 --> 02:25:56,372
You twist this into whatever you want.
You made a deal to save your ass.

1714
02:25:56,498 --> 02:25:58,833
You got our money,
three quarters of a million dollars of it,

1715
02:25:58,917 --> 02:26:01,252
you're still a hot-shot lawyer
and you're out of this.

1716
02:26:01,336 --> 02:26:02,545
I didn't keep a nickel of your money.

1717
02:26:02,671 --> 02:26:04,547
It was always for somebody else.

1718
02:26:04,673 --> 02:26:05,714
And, yeah,

1719
02:26:05,841 --> 02:26:08,300
I'm still a lawyer with references
from Bendini, Lambert & Locke.

1720
02:26:08,385 --> 02:26:11,220
You want to put that on your resume?

1721
02:26:11,346 --> 02:26:13,472
You think I'm ever gonna
turn on the ignition in my car again

1722
02:26:13,557 --> 02:26:14,682
without sweating?

1723
02:26:14,766 --> 02:26:18,227
Then I don't understand you.
What did you do it for?

1724
02:26:19,563 --> 02:26:20,938
You didn't win a thing.

1725
02:26:21,022 --> 02:26:25,276
Oh, yeah, I did. I won my life back.
You don't run me and they don't run me.

1726
02:26:26,361 --> 02:26:28,154
You want to know something weird?

1727
02:26:28,238 --> 02:26:31,824
I discovered the law again.
You actually made me think about it.

1728
02:26:31,908 --> 02:26:36,370
I managed to get through three years
of law school without doing that.

1729
02:26:38,540 --> 02:26:42,877
It's you at the dog track.
I could've gone public with it.

1730
02:26:42,961 --> 02:26:45,754
- Why didn't you?
- It's against the law.

1731
02:26:51,553 --> 02:26:52,970
Okay.

1732
02:26:55,891 --> 02:26:59,768
How in the hell
did you ever come up with mail fraud?

1733
02:27:01,062 --> 02:27:03,063
It was on the bar exam.

1734
02:27:04,441 --> 02:27:07,067
They made me study like hell for it.

1735
02:27:43,563 --> 02:27:47,650
Well, you've had a busy day.

1736
02:27:50,487 --> 02:27:52,154
So did you.

1737
02:27:54,658 --> 02:27:57,618
Why didn't you tell me the truth
about your plan?

1738
02:27:57,744 --> 02:27:59,787
All of it? The Moroltos.

1739
02:28:00,413 --> 02:28:04,124
Because I knew you'd worry,
and that might make you stay.

1740
02:28:05,460 --> 02:28:07,920
And I knew you needed to leave.

1741
02:28:18,014 --> 02:28:20,766
I like what you've done to the place.

1742
02:28:21,768 --> 02:28:24,979
- I thought you were going to your folks'.
- I was.

1743
02:28:27,357 --> 02:28:29,024
Some detour.

1744
02:28:32,612 --> 02:28:34,154
Where are you going?

1745
02:28:34,281 --> 02:28:35,990
To look for you.

1746
02:28:40,662 --> 02:28:44,957
I guess I didn't feel I could leave you
without trying to help you.

1747
02:28:48,503 --> 02:28:51,297
Do you want to tell me what happened?

1748
02:28:54,509 --> 02:28:56,176
Someday.

1749
02:28:58,179 --> 02:29:02,516
I think you should know
that Avery was pretty decent.

1750
02:29:05,353 --> 02:29:09,440
He was decent, and corrupt,

1751
02:29:09,524 --> 02:29:11,900
and ruined, and so unhappy...

1752
02:29:12,027 --> 02:29:13,068
Listen, Abby...

1753
02:29:13,194 --> 02:29:15,112
And it could have happened to you,
all of it.

1754
02:29:15,196 --> 02:29:16,697
You were on your way.

1755
02:29:16,823 --> 02:29:18,407
Did I lose you?

1756
02:29:25,373 --> 02:29:26,540
You look tired.

1757
02:29:26,666 --> 02:29:27,875
Did I?

1758
02:29:39,846 --> 02:29:42,056
I've loved you all my life.

1759
02:29:44,351 --> 02:29:46,143
Even before we met.

1760
02:29:48,897 --> 02:29:52,691
Part of it wasn't even you,
it was just a promise of you.

1761
02:29:54,027 --> 02:29:58,656
But these last days,
you kept your promise.

1762
02:30:06,331 --> 02:30:08,248
How could you lose me?

1763
02:30:41,199 --> 02:30:44,201
- You think it will make it?
- Make it where?

1764
02:30:45,537 --> 02:30:47,204
Boston.

1765
02:30:47,288 --> 02:30:49,039
What's in Boston?

1766
02:30:49,708 --> 02:30:51,041
We are.

1767
02:30:53,920 --> 02:30:57,047
And the Wong Boys, and my kids.

1768
02:30:58,883 --> 02:31:02,469
And a very small unknown law firm.

1769
02:31:02,554 --> 02:31:04,596
With a lot of potential.

1770
02:31:05,807 --> 02:31:07,057
Yeah.